v.0.2
=======

    Added sysmon screen, deprecated dot screen.
    Included auto completion support
    -- 2013-03-15 00:58 +1000, Bruno Braga <bruno.braga@gmail.com>

    Improved clock screen (support for am/pm)
    -- 2013-01-11 00:00 +0000, Shelby Jueden <shelbyjueden@gmail.com>

    Fixed #11 - Removed "x if y" syntax for python 2.5 support.
    Fixed #7 - randtxt crashed for long words
    Fixed #8 - asciiartfarts bad outpu on first/last lines
    Created plugin support.
    Fixed missing char in clock for number "2" ascii art.
    Cleaned HTML tags from rssfeed screensaver.
    -- 2012-04-19 21:13 +1000, Bruno Braga <bruno.braga@gmail.com>
     

v.0.1.1
=======

    Added packaging files for debian distribution.
    Added matrix screensaver.
    -- 2012-04-13 15:29 +1000, Bruno Braga <bruno.braga@gmail.com>
    

v.0.1
=====

    First released this code open-source. 
    -- 2012-03-01 17:29 +1000, Bruno Braga <bruno.braga@gmail.com>
